 A = \sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} - \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}
x\gg1
A
 \sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} + \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}
\frac{ \sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} - \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}}{1} \times \frac{\sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} + \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}}{\sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} + \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}} = \frac {\frac{4}{x}}{\sqrt {x + \frac {2}{x}} + \sqrt{x - \frac {2}{x}}} = \frac{2}{x\sqrt{x}}
A
\frac{1}{x\sqrt{x}} \text{ for }  x > \sqrt{\frac{2}{u}}
\frac{2}{x\sqrt{x}} \text{ for }  x > \sqrt{\frac{2}{u}}
\frac{1}{x\sqrt{x}} \text{ for }  x > \frac{2}{u}
\frac{2}{x\sqrt{x}} \text{ for }  x > \frac{1}{u}
